{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-21T00:28:34.289Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Anthropic's Prompt Improver"},{"type":"text","text":" is a console tool that takes your existing prompt template and "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"automatically enhances it using prompt engineering best practices"},{"type":"text","text":" like chain-of-thought reasoning, XML standardization, and prefill features. It boosts accuracy by "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"30% in classification tests"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Think of it as "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Claude improving your prompt for you\""},{"type":"text","text":" — an iterative refinement tool that applies professional techniques automatically."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What the Prompt Improver Does"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Core Capabilities"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"The prompt improver enhances existing prompts through several methods: chain-of-thought reasoning for systematic problem-solving, example standardisation using XML format, example enrichment with aligned reasoning, prompt rewriting for clarity, and prefill addition to direct Claude's actions and enforce output formats.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key techniques:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Chain-of-thought reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":" — Systematic problem-solving\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"XML standardization"},{"type":"text","text":" — Example formatting in XML\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example enrichment"},{"type":"text","text":" — Aligned reasoning with examples\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt rewriting"},{"type":"text","text":" — Clarity improvements\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prefill addition"},{"type":"text","text":" — Direct actions and enforce output formats"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Performance Results"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"30% Accuracy Boost"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Testing with Claude 3 Haiku involved matching article titles to a sentence pulled at random from 500 Wikipedia articles, where the prompt improver increased accuracy by 30% compared to the original prompt.\""}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"100% Word Count Adherence"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"In a separate test using ten Wikipedia articles, adherence to specific word count ranges for summaries reached 100% after using the prompt improver.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key metrics:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Classification accuracy:"},{"type":"text","text":" +30% improvement\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Word count adherence:"},{"type":"text","text":" 100% (vs. lower before)"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How to Use the Prompt Improver"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 1: Access the Prompt Improver"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"To get to the Anthropic prompt improver, go to your console dashboard at https://console.anthropic.com/dashboard and click on 'Improve an existing prompt'.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Requirements:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Need an account for the platform console"},{"type":"text","text":" — Pay for tokens, not just chat subscription\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Go to dashboard"},{"type":"text","text":" — "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"console.anthropic.com/dashboard"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Click \"Improve an existing prompt\""},{"type":"text","text":" — Launch the tool"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 2: Create Your Initial Prompt"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"You can fill in a first version of your prompt in template form. It needs to have a variable in double curly braces.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Template format:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Analyze this artwork: {{artwork_description}}\n\nInstructions:\n- Identify the main subject\n- Describe the style\n- Note any interesting details"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key requirement:"},{"type":"text","text":" Must include a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"variable in double curly braces"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"{{input}}"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"{{artwork_description}}"},{"type":"text","text":")"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 3: Review and Refine Claude's Improvements"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"After filling in your draft prompt, Claude will have a first pass at improving it. In my example, the output format clarification seems useful, but the prompt seems rather long. I would probably click on 'Improve prompt' and tell Claude to be more concise for the next version.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Process:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Review the improved prompt"},{"type":"text","text":" — Claude applies enhancements\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Check what changed"},{"type":"text","text":" — Output format clarification, XML tags, etc.\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Iterate if needed"},{"type":"text","text":" — Ask for more concise, more detailed, etc.\n4. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Click \"Improve prompt\""},{"type":"text","text":" — Generate another version"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example iteration:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Version 1:"},{"type":"text","text":" \"The prompt seems rather long\" → Ask for conciseness\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Version 2:"},{"type":"text","text":" More concise, but still well-structured\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Version 3:"},{"type":"text","text":" Final optimized version"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 4: Add Examples for Better Output Formatting"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"To further clarify what type of output format and style you are expecting, you can add examples. You can directly generate an output, which can be helpful as a starting point, if only to see how your current prompt could be misunderstood by the model.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Why add examples:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Clarify output format"},{"type":"text","text":" — Show exactly what you want\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Clarify style"},{"type":"text","text":" — Set tone and voice\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prevent misunderstandings"},{"type":"text","text":" — See how model interprets prompt\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Generate starting point"},{"type":"text","text":" — Use AI-generated output as example"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example addition:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<examples>\n<example>\nInput: \"A painting of a sunset over mountains\"\nOutput:\n- Subject: Sunset landscape\n- Style: Realistic, warm colors\n- Details: Golden light, mountain silhouettes, peaceful atmosphere\n</example>\n\n<example>\nInput: \"A portrait of an elderly woman\"\nOutput:\n- Subject: Human portrait\n- Style: Classical, detailed shading\n- Details: Wrinkles showing age, expression full of wisdom, soft lighting\n</example>\n</examples>"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 5: Test with Multiple Inputs"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"You should also test your prompts on as many inputs as possible. In the evaluate tab, you can add test cases to run through with each new prompt version.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Testing process:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Go to \"Evaluate\" tab"},{"type":"text","text":" — Access evaluation interface\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Add test cases"},{"type":"text","text":" — Create input examples\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Add \"ideal answers\""},{"type":"text","text":" — What you expect the output to be\n4. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Score results"},{"type":"text","text":" — Grade on 5-point scale\n5. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Compare versions"},{"type":"text","text":" — See how improved prompt performs vs. original"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example test case:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Input: {{artwork_description}} = \"A photograph of a busy city street at night\"\n\nIdeal Answer:\n- Subject: Urban street scene\n- Style: High contrast, realistic photography\n- Details: Bright lights, blurred motion, neon signs, pedestrians\n\nActual Output: [from improved prompt]\nScore: [5-point scale]"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 6: Generate More Test Cases"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"You can also generate more test cases, which can help speed up the process of creating a test set.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefit:"},{"type":"text","text":" AI automatically creates diverse test inputs, speeding up evaluation setup."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The Evaluation Tool"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"5-Point Scoring System"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"The system also includes an 'ideal output' column in the Evaluations tab to help users grade model outputs on a 5-point scale.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Scoring guide:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"5/5"},{"type":"text","text":" — Perfect match with ideal output\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"4/5"},{"type":"text","text":" — Very good, minor differences\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"3/5"},{"type":"text","text":" — Acceptable, but noticeable gaps\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"2/5"},{"type":"text","text":" — Poor, missing key elements\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"1/5"},{"type":"text","text":" — Failed completely"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"LLM-Based Auto-Grading"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"You can add the 'ideal' answers and score the results, which could be used to collaborate between teams, or even score future prompt versions automatically with an LLM.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Auto-grading:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Manual scoring"},{"type":"text","text":" — Humans grade outputs\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Auto scoring"},{"type":"text","text":" — LLM grades outputs automatically\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Team collaboration"},{"type":"text","text":" — Share scores across teams"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Version History"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"The model settings and prompt versions are recorded for future reference.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Track improvements"},{"type":"text","text":" — See how each version changed\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Compare versions"},{"type":"text","text":" — A/B test different prompts\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Revert if needed"},{"type":"text","text":" — Go back to previous version"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example Management Feature"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Structured Format in Workbench"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"The new example management feature allows developers to manage examples in a structured format directly in the Workbench.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Features:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"XML format"},{"type":"text","text":" — Standardized example structure\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Direct management"},{"type":"text","text":" — Edit in the console\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Aligned reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":" — Examples include reasoning steps"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Synthetic Example Generation"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"For prompts without examples, Claude can automatically generate synthetic example inputs and draft outputs.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"How it works:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Detect no examples"},{"type":"text","text":" — Prompt lacks few-shot examples\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Generate inputs"},{"type":"text","text":" — Create realistic test inputs\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Generate outputs"},{"type":"text","text":" — Create ideal responses for each input\n4. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Add to prompt"},{"type":"text","text":" — Integrate into prompt template"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"For a prompt analyzing product reviews, Claude generates:\n\n<examples>\n<example>\nInput: \"This phone is amazing! Battery lasts all day and camera is crystal clear.\"\nOutput: Sentiment: Positive, Rating: 5/5, Key points: Battery life, Camera quality\n</example>\n\n<example>\nInput: \"Terrible experience. The screen broke after 2 days and customer service was unhelpful.\"\nOutput: Sentiment: Negative, Rating: 1/5, Key points: Screen durability, Customer service\n</example>\n</examples>"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Real-World Use Cases"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use Case 1: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Artwork Analysis"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example from documentation:"},{"type":"text","text":" \"Analyze this artwork: {{artwork_description}}\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Original prompt:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Analyze this artwork: {{artwork_description}}\n\nInstructions:\n- Identify the main subject\n- Describe the style\n- Note any interesting details"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"After Prompt Improver:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Analyze the following artwork description: {{artwork_description}}\n\n<chain_of_thought>\n1. First, read the description carefully to understand what's being depicted\n2. Identify the main subject by looking for the most prominent element\n3. Analyze artistic style by examining descriptors of technique, color, and composition\n4. Note specific details that make the artwork unique or interesting\n</chain_of_thought>\n\n<output_format>\nSubject: [clear identification]\nStyle: [artistic classification with evidence]\nDetails: [bullet list of 3-5 notable features]\n</output_format>\n\n<examples>\n<example>\nInput: \"A painting of a sunset over mountains with golden light\"\nOutput:\nSubject: Sunset landscape\nStyle: Realistic, warm color palette\nDetails:\n- Golden light creating atmosphere\n- Mountain silhouettes in foreground\n- Peaceful, serene mood\n</example>\n</examples>\n\n<prefill>\nSubject:\n</prefill>"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Improvements:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- ✅ Chain-of-thought added\n- ✅ XML tags for structure\n- ✅ Output format specified\n- ✅ Example added\n- ✅ Prefill to enforce format"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use Case 2: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Article-to-Sentence Matching"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Test case:"},{"type":"text","text":" \"Matching article titles to a sentence pulled at random from 500 Wikipedia articles\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Result:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"30% accuracy boost"},{"type":"text","text":" after using Prompt Improver"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use Case 3: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Summary Word Count Control"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Test case:"},{"type":"text","text":" \"Summary word count ranges for ten Wikipedia articles\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Result:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"100% adherence"},{"type":"text","text":" to word count after using Prompt Improver"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prompt Improver vs. Prompt Generator"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Feature"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt Improver"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt Generator"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Input"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Your existing prompt template"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Task description"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Output"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Improved version of your prompt"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"New prompt from scratch"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use case"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Refine and optimize existing prompts"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Create new prompts"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Improves"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Your draft prompt"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"N/A (creates from scratch)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"K